OL,3,CTeenage boy 'died in terror' after dad
OL,4,Chigh on cocaine crashed van
OL,6,FA cocaine-fuelled motorist who killed
OL,7,Fhis teenage son after he ignored
OL,8,Fmedical advice to stop driving has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed for 10 years.
OL,11,FDaniel Burba, 31, had an epileptic fit
OL,12,Fat the wheel of his wife's Peugeot van
OL,13,Fwhich swerved off the M6 near
OL,14,FLancaster and hit a tree on April 20.
OL,16,FHis front-seat passenger, Ryan Morgan,
OL,17,F14, sustained head injuries and was
OL,18,Fpronounced dead at the scene of the
OL,19,Fcollision on the southbound
OL,20,Fcarriageway between junctions 34 and
OL,21,F33.
