OL,3,CTeenage boy 'died in terror' after dad
OL,4,Chigh on cocaine crashed van
OL,6,FThe youngster died "in terror" as he
OL,7,Ftried to gain control of the vehicle
OL,8,Fmoments before the crash, Preston
OL,9,FCrown Court heard.
OL,11,FBurba was taken to hospital with
OL,12,F"relatively minor" injuries to his
OL,13,Fribs and lacerations.
OL,15,FWhile he was being treated, a
OL,16,Fparamedic discovered a small bag of
OL,17,Fcocaine in Burba's wallet, the court
OL,18,Fwas told.
