OL,3,CTeenage boy 'died in terror' after dad
OL,4,Chigh on cocaine crashed van
OL,6,FBlood tests revealed that the
OL,7,Fdefendant was four times above the
OL,8,Flegal drug-drive limit.
OL,10,FIt emerged that Burba, from Morecambe,
OL,11,FLancashire, had been told in October
OL,12,F2014 by his doctor to stop taking
OL,13,Fcocaine after he suffered a seizure
OL,14,Fwhich lasted up to four minutes.
OL,16,FThe provisional licence holder was
OL,17,Falso advised not to drive.
