OL,6,FBurba was given a similar warning in
OL,7,FFebruary when he was admitted to
OL,8,Fhospital after more fits and was also
OL,9,Ftold to inform the DVLA.
OL,11,FSentencing, Judge Robert Altham, the
OL,12,FHonorary Recorder of Preston, told
OL,13,Fhim: "You knew that cocaine
OL,14,Fpredisposed you to further fits.
OL,16,F"You were not entitled to drive
OL,17,Funsupervised and certainly not on the
OL,18,Fmotorway. You should not have behind
OL,19,Fthe wheel at all
