OL,6,F"No sentence will ever make up for the
OL,7,Floss of life particularly in these
OL,8,Fcircumstances. " he said.
OL,10,F"Daniel Burba will have the rest of
OL,11,Fhis life to reflect on the
OL,12,Fcatastrophic consequences his decision
OL,13,Fto consume drugs and then get behind
OL,14,Fthe wheel have had.
OL,16,F"Sadly his son Ryan Morgan will not"
OL,18,FBurba, of Arnside Crescent, pleaded
OL,19,Fguilty at an earlier hearing to
OL,20,Fcausing death by dangerous driving.
